## Project structure

```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/           # Login, signup
│   ├── api/              # API routes
│   │   ├── ai/           # TTS, STT, dialogue, questions, scoring
│   │   ├── auth/         # Auth sync
│   │   ├── candidate/    # Profile, saved jobs, persona, confidence
│   │   ├── candidates/   # Candidate creation
│   │   ├── employer/     # Jobs, applications, reports, distribution
│   │   ├── jobs/         # Job CRUD, apply
│   │   ├── applications/ # Application session start, resume-fit
│   │   ├── sessions/     # Interview session, stages, answers, focus, tools, complete
│   │   └── health/       # DB health check
│   ├── candidate/        # Job list, profile, interview, completed, settings
│   ├── employer/         # Dashboard, jobs (new, detail), job wizard
│   ├── jobs/             # Public job view by publicId
│   ├── jobBoard/         # Job board
│   ├── post-a-job/       # Post job flow
│   ├── lib/              # App-level utilities
│   └── page.tsx          # Home (role-based redirect)
├── components/           # Shared UI (auth-nav, pipeline-demo, site-logo, ui/)
├── frontend/
│   ├── components/       # Additional components
│   └── hooks/            # Shared hooks
├── database/
│   ├── migrations/       # SQL migrations (e.g. add-candidate-saved-jobs.sql)
│   ├── verify-db.mjs     # DB verification script
│   └── run-migration-saved-jobs.mjs
├── src/                  # Genkit AI source (e.g. dev.ts, flows)
├── tests/                # Vitest API tests
├── public/               # Static assets (e.g. logos)
├── .env                  # Optional env (e.g. API keys for AI/voice)
├── .env.local            # Supabase + secrets (do not commit)
└── package.json
```

---

## API overview

- **Auth:** `POST /api/auth/sync` — sync user/roles after login.
- **Jobs:** `GET/POST /api/jobs`, `GET/PATCH /api/jobs/[jobId]`, `POST /api/jobs/[jobId]/apply`.
- **Employer:** `GET/POST /api/employer/jobs`, `GET/PATCH /api/employer/jobs/[jobId]`, `GET /api/employer/jobs/[jobId]/applications`, `GET /api/employer/jobs/[jobId]/distribution`, `GET /api/employer/applications/[applicationId]/report`.
- **Candidate:** `GET/POST /api/candidate/profile`, `GET/POST/DELETE /api/candidate/saved-jobs`, `GET /api/candidate/saved-jobs/[jobId]`.
- **Applications:** `POST /api/applications/[applicationId]/session/start`, `POST /api/applications/[applicationId]/resume-fit`.
- **Sessions:** `GET/PATCH /api/sessions/[sessionId]`, `POST /api/sessions/[sessionId]/complete`, `POST /api/sessions/[sessionId]/abandon`, focus-event, stages/next, stages/[stageSessionId]/question, answer, case, code, tool-usage.
- **AI:** `POST /api/ai/text-to-speech`, `POST /api/ai/speech-to-text`, `POST /api/ai/interviewer-dialogue`, `POST /api/ai/generate-followup`, `POST /api/ai/generate-questions`, `POST /api/ai/score-answer`.
- **Health:** `GET /api/health/db`.

---

## Database (Supabase)

Core tables used by the app (see `database/verify-db.mjs` and schema SQL):

- **Identity & roles:** `users`, `user_roles`, `employer_profiles`
- **Jobs:** `job_profiles`, `job_stages`, `stage_question_bank`, `job_distribution_status`, `public_job_views`
- **Candidates:** `job_applications`, `candidates` (if still used)
- **Interview:** `interview_sessions`, `focus_events`, `tool_usage_logs`, `stage_scores`, `question_scores`
- **Reports:** `reports` (optional, for employer report generation)

Run `npm run db:verify` after applying schema to confirm all required tables exist.

