## Roadmap and gaps

See **`improvements.md`** for:

- Distribution lifecycle (update/close flows, demo seeding).
- Job builder UX (stepper/tabs: Overview, Stages, Question Bank, Distribution).
- Candidate apply flow aligned with `job_applications` and real job profile.
- Employer job detail: real candidates list and report links.
- Interview: join flow, meeting layout, speech pipeline, focus policies, session persistence.
- AI: rubric/stage plan, question engine, resume fit, tools panel, scoring.
- Reports and distribution UI, plus end-to-end demo seeding.

